msgstr "authselect(8)"

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "NAME"
msgstr "ຊື່"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:9
msgid "authselect - select system identity and authentication sources."
msgstr "authselect - ເລືອກແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຕົນ ແລະ ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງລະບົບ."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "SYNOPSIS"
msgstr "ຮູບແບບການໃຊ້ງານ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid " authselect [--debug] [--trace] [--warn] command [command options]\n"
msgstr " authselect [--debug] [--trace] [--warn] ຄຳສັ່ງ [ຕົວເລືອກຄຳສັ່ງ]\n"

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "ຄຳອະທິບາຍ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"*Authselect* is a tool to configure system identity and authentication sources\n"
"and providers by selecting a specific profile. Profile is a set of files that\n"
"describes how the resulting system configuration will look like. When a profile\n"
"is selected, *authselect* will create nsswitch.conf(5) and PAM(8) stack to use\n"
"identity and authentication sources defined by the profile.\n"
msgstr ""
"*Authselect* ແມ່ນເຄື່ອງມືສຳລັບກຳນົດຄ່າແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຕົນ ແລະ ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງລະບົບ\n"
"ລວມທັງຜູ້ໃຫ້ບໍລິການ ໂດຍການເລືອກໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ສະເພາະເຈາະຈົງ. ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ແມ່ນຊຸດຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່\n"
"ອະທິບາຍວ່າການກຳນົດຄ່າລະບົບທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບນັ້ນຈະມີລັກສະນະແນວໃດ. ເມື່ອມີການເລືອກໂປຣໄຟລ໌,\n"
"*authselect* ຈະສ້າງ nsswitch.conf(5) ແລະ PAM(8) stack ເພື່ອໃຊ້\n"
"ແຫຼ່ງຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຕົນ ແລະ ການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໂດຍໂປຣໄຟລ໌.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:27
msgid ""
"If the provided profile set is not sufficient, the administrator may create "
"a custom profile by putting it in a special profile directory "
"({AUTHSELECT_CUSTOM_DIR}). By doing so, the profile is immediately usable by "
"*authselect*. See _authselect-profiles(5)_ for more information on extending "
"existing profiles."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າຫາກຊຸດໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີໃຫ້ຍັງບໍ່ພຽງພໍ, ຜູ້ດູແລລະບົບສາມາດສ້າງໂປຣໄຟລ໌ກຳນົດເອງໄດ້ໂດຍການເກັບໄວ້ໃນ ໄດເຣັກທໍ"
"ຣີໂປຣໄຟລ໌ພິເສດ ({AUTHSELECT_CUSTOM_DIR}). ເມື່ອເຮັດແນວນັ້ນ, ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ຈະສາມາດ ໃຊ້ງານໄດ້ທັນທີໂ"
"ດຍ *authselect*. ເບິ່ງ _authselect-profiles(5)_ ສຳລັບຂໍ້ມູນເພີ່ມເຕີມກ່ຽວກັບການຂະຫຍາຍ ໂປຣ"
"ໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີຢູ່."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "OPT-IN TO AUTHSELECT"
msgstr "ການເລືອກໃຊ້ AUTHSELECT"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:39
msgid ""
"Authselect will not touch your existing configuration unless it has already "
"been created by it. If you want to start using authselect to configure your "
"system authentication, please call *authselect select* with *--force* "
"parameter first (e.g. *authselect select sssd --force*). The *--force* "
"parameter tells authselect that it is all right to overwrite existing non-"
"authselect configuration (see description below). Using the *--force* "
"parameter will automatically generate a backup of your current configuration "
"so if you wish to go back you can restore it with *authselect backup-"
"restore* command (see description below)."
msgstr ""
"Authselect ຈະບໍ່ແຕະຕ້ອງກັບການກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ມີຢູ່ຂອງທ່ານ ນອກຈາກວ່າມັນໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນໂດຍຕົວມັນເອງ. ຖ້າທ່ານ"
"ຕ້ອງການເລີ່ມໃຊ້ authselect ເພື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າການຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງລະບົບ, ກະລຸນາໃຊ້ຄຳສັ່ງ *authselect "
"select* ພ້ອມກັບພາຣາມິເຕີ *--force* ກ່ອນ (ຕົວຢ່າງ: *authselect select sssd --force*)"
". ພາຣາມິເຕີ *--force* ຈະບອກ authselect ວ່າອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ຂຽນທັບການກຳນົດຄ່າເດີມທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ມາຈາກ "
"authselect (ເບິ່ງຄຳອະທິບາຍດ້ານລຸ່ມ). ການໃຊ້ພາຣາມິເຕີ *--force* ຈະເຮັດການສຳຮອງຂໍ້ມູນ ການກຳນົ"
"ດຄ່າປັດຈຸບັນຂອງທ່ານໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ດັ່ງນັ້ນຖ້າທ່ານຕ້ອງການກັບຄືນຄ່າເດີມ ທ່ານສາມາດ ກູ້ຄືນໄດ້ດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ "
"*authselect backup-restore* (ເບິ່ງຄຳອະທິບາຍດ້ານລຸ່ມ)."

#. type: Title -
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "AVAILABLE COMMANDS"
msgstr "ຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ງານ"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:44
msgid ""
"To list all available commands run *authselect* without any parameters.  To "
"print help for the selected command run *authselect COMMAND --help*."
msgstr ""
"ເພື່ອເບິ່ງລາຍຊື່ຄຳສັ່ງທັງໝົດທີ່ມີໃຫ້ ໃຫ້ລັນ *authselect* ໂດຍບໍ່ຕ້ອງໃສ່ພາຣາມິເຕີໃດໆ. ເພື່ອເບິ່ງວິທີການໃຊ້ງາ"
"ນຂອງຄຳສັ່ງທີ່ເລືອກ ໃຫ້ລັນ *authselect ຄຳສັ່ງ --help*."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:45
#, no-wrap
msgid "*select* profile_id [features] [-f, --force] [-q, --quiet] [-b] [--backup=NAME]"
msgstr ""
"*select* profile_id [features] [-f, --force] [-q, --quiet] [-b] [--"
"backup=NAME]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:48
msgid ""
"Activate desired profile. See profile description with *show* command, to "
"list profile specific optional features."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດໃຊ້ງານໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ຕ້ອງການ. ເບິ່ງຄຳອະທິບາຍໂປຣໄຟລ໌ດ້ວຍຄຳສັ່ງ *show*, ເພື່ອເບິ່ງລາຍຊື່ ຄຸນສົມບັດເສີມສ"
"ະເພາະຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌ນັ້ນໆ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--force, -f*"
msgstr "*--force, -f*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:54
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Write changes even if the previous configuration was not created by\n"
"authselect but by other tool or by manual changes. This option will\n"
"automatically backup system files before writing any change unless\n"
"*--nobackup* option is set.\n"
msgstr ""
"ຂຽນການປ່ຽນແປງລົງໄປ ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າການກຳນົດຄ່າກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້ບໍ່ໄດ້ຖືກສ້າງໂດຍ\n"
"authselect ແຕ່ມາຈາກເຄື່ອງມືອື່ນ ຫຼື ຈາກການປ່ຽນແປງດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ. ຕົວເລືອກນີ້ຈະ\n"
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດກ່ອນທີ່ຈະຂຽນການປ່ຽນແປງໃດໆ ນອກຈາກວ່າ\n"
"ຈະມີການຕັ້ງຕົວເລືອກ *--nobackup* ໄວ້.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:55 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:80
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:149 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:167
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-b*"
msgstr "*-b*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:60
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before activating the selected profile. The backup\n"
"will be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with\n"
"unique string is used as a name of the backup. This is a shortcut\n"
"for *--backup=*.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະເປີດໃຊ້ງານໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ\n"
"ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບ\n"
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ຂອງການສຳຮອງ. ນີ້ແມ່ນທາງລັດ\n"
"ສຳລັບ *--backup=*.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:61 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:86
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:155 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:173
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--backup=NAME*"
msgstr "*--backup=NAME*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:65
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before activating the selected profile. The backup\n"
"will be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with\n"
"unique string is used as a name if no value is provided.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະເປີດໃຊ້ງານໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ\n"
"ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບ\n"
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ ຖ້າຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດຄ່າໃດໆ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--nobackup*"
msgstr "*--nobackup*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "Do not backup system configuration even if *--force* is set.\n"
msgstr ""
"ບໍ່ຕ້ອງສຳຮອງຂໍ້ມູນການກຳນົດຄ່າລະບົບ ເຖິງແມ່ນວ່າຈະຕັ້ງ *--force* ໄວ້ກໍຕາມ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:69 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:160
#, no-wrap
msgid "*--quiet, -q*"
msgstr "*--quiet, -q*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:72 src/man/authselect.8.adoc:163
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"The command will not print any informational message such as additional\n"
"profile requirements or backup location. Errors are still being print.\n"
msgstr ""
"ຄຳສັ່ງຈະບໍ່ສະແດງຂໍ້ຄວາມຂໍ້ມູນໃດໆ ເຊັ່ນ ຂໍ້ກຳນົດເພີ່ມເຕີມຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌\n"
"ຫຼື ສະຖານທີ່ເກັບຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ. ແຕ່ຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຍັງຄົງຈະຖືກສະແດງຢູ່.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:73
#, no-wrap
msgid "*apply-changes* [-b] [--backup=NAME]"
msgstr "*apply-changes* [-b] [--backup=NAME]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:79
msgid ""
"Re-apply currently selected profile. If the profile templates were updated "
"this command can be used to regenerate current system configuration in order "
"to apply these changes on the system. This command will only re-apply the "
"changes if the existing configuration is a valid authselect configuration, "
"otherwise an error is returned."
msgstr ""
"ນຳໃຊ້ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກໄວ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນຄືນໃໝ່. ຖ້າມີການອັບເດດແມ່ແບບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ສາມາດ ໃຊ້ເພື່ອສ້າງການກຳ"
"ນົດຄ່າລະບົບປັດຈຸບັນໃໝ່ ເພື່ອນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງເຫຼົ່ານັ້ນລົງໃນລະບົບ. ຄຳສັ່ງນີ້ຈະນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງຄືນໃໝ່ກໍຕໍ່ເມື່ອກ"
"ານກຳນົດຄ່າທີ່ມີຢູ່ນັ້ນເປັນການກຳນົດຄ່າຂອງ authselect ທີ່ຖືກຕ້ອງເທົ່ານັ້ນ, ບໍ່ດັ່ງນັ້ນຈະສົ່ງຄ່າຂໍ້ຜິດພາດຄືນມາ."

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:85
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before applying changes. The backup\n"
"will be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with\n"
"unique string is used as a name of the backup. This is a shortcut\n"
"for *--backup=*.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງ\n"
"ຈະຖືກເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບ\n"
"ຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ຂອງການສຳຮອງ. ນີ້ແມ່ນທາງລັດ\n"
"ສຳລັບ *--backup=*.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:90
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Backup system files before applying changes. The backup will\n"
"be stored at {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. Current time with unique\n"
"string is used as a name if no value is provided.\n"
msgstr ""
"ສຳຮອງໄຟລ໌ລະບົບກ່ອນທີ່ຈະນຳໃຊ້ການປ່ຽນແປງ. ຂໍ້ມູນສຳຮອງຈະຖືກ\n"
"ເກັບໄວ້ທີ່ {AUTHSELECT_BACKUP_DIR}/NAME. ເວລາປັດຈຸບັນພ້ອມກັບຂໍ້ຄວາມທີ່ບໍ່ຊ້ຳກັນ\n"
"ຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເປັນຊື່ ຖ້າຫາກບໍ່ໄດ້ກຳນົດຄ່າໃດໆ.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:91
#, no-wrap
msgid "*list*"
msgstr "*list*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:93
msgid "List available profiles."
msgstr "ສະແດງລາຍຊື່ໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ມີໃຫ້ໃຊ້ງານ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "*list-features* profile_id"
msgstr "*list-features* profile_id"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:98
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"List all features available in given profile.\n"
"_Note:_ This will only list the features without any description. Please, read the profile documentation with *show* to see what the features do."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງລາຍຊື່ຄຸນສົມບັດທັງໝົດທີ່ມີໃນໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ກຳນົດ.\n"
"_ໝາຍເຫດ:_ ນີ້ຈະສະແດງພຽງແຕ່ລາຍຊື່ຄຸນສົມບັດໂດຍບໍ່ມີຄຳອະທິບາຍ. ກະລຸນາອ່ານ ເອກະສານຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌ດ້ວຍຄ"
"ຳສັ່ງ *show* ເພື່ອເບິ່ງວ່າແຕ່ລະຄຸນສົມບັດໃຊ້ເຮັດຫຍັງ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:99
#, no-wrap
msgid "*show* profile_id"
msgstr "*show* profile_id"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:101
msgid "Print information about the profile."
msgstr "ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບໂປຣໄຟລ໌."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "*requirements* profile_id [features]"
msgstr "*requirements* profile_id [features]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:104
msgid "Print information about profile requirements."
msgstr "ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບຂໍ້ກຳນົດຂອງໂປຣໄຟລ໌."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:105
#, no-wrap
msgid "*current* [-r, --raw]"
msgstr "*current* [-r, --raw]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:109
msgid ""
"Print information about currently selected profiles. If *--raw* option is "
"specified, the command will print raw parameters as they were passed to "
"*select* command instead of formatted output."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບໂປຣໄຟລ໌ທີ່ເລືອກໃຊ້ໃນປັດຈຸບັນ. ຖ້າລະບຸຕົວເລືອກ *--raw*, ຄຳສັ່ງຈະສະແດງ ພາຣາມິເຕີດິບ"
"ຕາມທີ່ຖືກສົ່ງໃຫ້ຄຳສັ່ງ *select* ແທນການສະແດງຜົນໃນຮູບແບບປົກກະຕິ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "*check*"
msgstr "*check*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:114
msgid ""
"Check if the current configuration is valid (it was either created by "
"*authselect* or there are no leftovers from previous authselect "
"configuration)."
msgstr ""
"ກວດສອບວ່າການກຳນົດຄ່າປັດຈຸບັນຖືກຕ້ອງຫຼືບໍ່ (ບໍ່ວ່າຈະຖືກສ້າງໂດຍ *authselect* ຫຼື ບໍ່ມີສ່ວນເສດເຫຼືອຈາກການ"
"ກຳນົດຄ່າ authselect ກ່ອນໜ້ານີ້)."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:115
#, no-wrap
msgid "*test* profile_id [options] [features]"
msgstr "*test* profile_id [options] [features]"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:118
msgid ""
"Print content of files generated by *authselect* without actually writing "
"anything to system configuration."
msgstr ""
"ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງໄຟລ໌ທີ່ສ້າງໂດຍ *authselect* ໂດຍທີ່ຍັງບໍ່ໄດ້ຂຽນຂໍ້ມູນໃດໆ ລົງໃນການກຳນົດຄ່າຂອງລະບົບແ"
"ທ້ໆ."

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:119
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-a, --all*"
msgstr "*-a, --all*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Print content of all files.\n"
msgstr "ສະແດງເນື້ອໃນຂອງທຸກໄຟລ໌.\n"

#. type: Labeled list
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:122
#, no-wrap
msgid "*-n, --nsswitch*"
msgstr "*-n, --nsswitch*"

#. type: Plain text
#: src/man/authselect.8.adoc:124
